%% E057 - IndexerWorker steps sequence - F1-5 Pipeline
%% Source: docs/design/f1-5-indexer.md (E056)
sequenceDiagram
    participant QI as queue-indexer
    participant IW as IndexerWorker
    participant Repo as IRulingRepository
    participant SQL as Azure SQL
    participant Blob as Blob Storage
    participant Emb as EmbeddingService
    participant Search as Azure AI Search

    QI->>IW: IndexerMessage
    IW->>Repo: ExistsByContentHashAsync(contentHash)
    Repo->>SQL: SELECT 1 FROM Rulings WHERE ContentHash=?
    SQL-->>Repo: exists
    Repo-->>IW: true/false
    alt ContentHash exists
        IW->>IW: Discard message, exit
    else ContentHash not exists
        IW->>SQL: PersistRulingStep (Rulings, Courts, Judges, etc.)
        SQL-->>IW: RulingId
        IW->>Blob: UploadBlobStep (verify exists)
        Blob-->>IW: ok
        IW->>Emb: GenerateEmbeddingsStep (summary+holding, chunks)
        Emb-->>IW: ruling embedding, chunk embeddings
        IW->>Search: IndexSearchStep (rulings-by-ruling, rulings-by-chunk)
        Search-->>IW: ok
        IW->>SQL: ResolveCitationsStep (inbound + outbound)
        SQL-->>IW: ok
    end
